Enum Class BottleSize

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<BottleSize>
eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.data.BottleSize
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<BottleSize>, Constable
public enum BottleSize extends Enum<BottleSize>
This `BottleSize` enum represents the possible bottle sizes of the wine.

Each enum instance is associated with a specific volume corresponding to the size of the wine bottle. The volume for each bottle size is provided in centiliters.

This enum provides a static method `doubleToBottleSize`, which takes a double representing a volume and returns the corresponding `BottleSize` instance.
